ative benefits to manage large numbers of smart\nentities, and to enable attributes and alerts inheritance for fine-grained\nsecurity authorization policies. We present proof of concept implementation of\nour model in AWS cloud platform demonstrating real-world uses cases along with\nperformance metrics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Aug 2019 20:47:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-23"}
