e proton\nspectra for $\\theta_{\\rm nB} = 15^\\circ$ and $45^\\circ$ are similar as a result\nof the competition of the effectiveness of the shock drift acceleration and the\ndiffusive shock acceleration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2019 02:11:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
