icantly degrade the performance of the dynamic\neco-routing navigation when the traffic density is high. It also shows that the\nfuel consumption can be increased due to lack of communication reliability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2019 07:14:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-23"}
