 important step towards unraveling the physics behind supergranules, as we\nstart appreciating the parameters that we may reliably infer from a\ntime-distance helioseismic inversion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2019 15:33:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
